    "name": "Grimstone Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 3158620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/2f4f0fae55277318b9e075b93bd9b935.avif?t=1737119573\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras_big/2f4f0fae55277318b9e075b93bd9b935.avif?t=1737119573 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[主要功能 </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D自上而下roguelite体验：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3D自上而下深度射击游戏为roguelite类型注入了新的活力。在这场冒险中，死亡不是终点，每一个新的开始都会让你变得更加强大。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略武器组合：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 双手各持不同武器，根据自己的游戏风格塑造战场。使用远程武器从远处追击敌人，而另一只手则使用近战武器为突然袭击做好准备。每种武器组合都具有不同的战略优势，快来发现最致命的武器组合吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性化技能树：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从各种技能中进行选择，形成自己独特的游戏风格。无论你是增加体力的生命消耗专家，还是用快速攻击消灭敌人，你选择的每种技能都会让你独一无二。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满活力和惊喜的战场：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 短期事件可以在眨眼之间扭转战局。通过使用炮塔或生命塔来获得对敌人的战术优势。巧妙利用战场是生存的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战略资源管理:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 市场为您提供不同的路径。从市场上购买临时能量补充剂可立即获得优势。明智地管理资源将帮助您在充满挑战的关卡中生存下来。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9afef330112311264402d73e57571110.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=772 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9afef330112311264402d73e57571110.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9afef330112311264402d73e57571110.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限重放:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏中的关卡、敌人和物品都是随机生成的，每次游戏体验都不尽相同。每一次您都将面临新的挑战，并制定不同的策略来探索《灰石幸存者》的深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度层:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >子弹/药水： 有几率为玩家的子弹赋予独特属性。 <br><br>装弹： 每次装填武器或使用道具时，都能获得不同的属性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步数： 当你行走时，你的步伐会变得神奇。 <br><br>闪避/跳跃： 在闪避或招架时提高速度的能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺和短跑： 奔跑时在身后留下痕迹。 <br><br>按钮/互动装置： 当达到一定的伤害临界值时，会出现具有独特属性的按钮。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近战 影响近战武器的能量加成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远程： 影响远程武器的强力装备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >市场： 在市场中提供折扣的破旧令牌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可穿戴设备： 用可视服装定制你的角色。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1737119573\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158620/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1737119573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
